title: Integrating artificial intelligence and quantum computing: A systematic literature review of features and applications
journal: International Journal of Cognitive Computing in Engineering
abstract: This paper presents a comprehensive systematic literature review on the integration of artificial intelligence and quantum computing, exploring their combined features and applications across various domains.

title: Artificial Intelligence Applications in Musculoskeletal Imaging
abstract: This review explores the latest applications of artificial intelligence in musculoskeletal imaging, focusing on diagnostic accuracy, treatment planning, and clinical outcomes.

title: Deep Learning-Assisted Organogel Pressure Sensor for Alphabet Recognition and Bio-Mechanical Motion Monitoring
abstract: We present a deep learning-assisted organogel pressure sensor capable of alphabet recognition and bio-mechanical motion monitoring with high accuracy and real-time performance.

title: MpoxNet: Leveraging hybrid deep learning for enhanced monkeypox diagnosis and risk identification
journal: International Journal of Cognitive Computing in Engineering
abstract: MpoxNet introduces a hybrid deep learning framework for improved monkeypox diagnosis and risk identification, combining computer vision and clinical data analysis.

title: Development of a feature vector for accurate breast cancer detection in mammographic images
journal: International Journal of Cognitive Computing in Engineering
abstract: This research develops a novel feature vector approach for accurate breast cancer detection in mammographic images using advanced machine learning techniques.

title: Transforming legal texts into computational logic: Enhancing next generation public sector automation through explainable AI decision support
journal: International Journal of Cognitive Computing in Engineering
abstract: This paper presents a framework for transforming legal texts into computational logic using explainable AI for public sector automation and decision support systems.

title: A DistilBERT-based hierarchical text classification for traffic analysis
journal: International Journal of Cognitive Computing in Engineering
abstract: We propose a DistilBERT-based hierarchical text classification system for traffic analysis, achieving high accuracy with reduced computational requirements.

title: Multi-head Spectral-attentive Residual Generative Adversarial Network: A High-fidelity Generative Adversarial Network Based Model for Image Haze Removal
journal: International Journal of Engineering Transactions B Applications
abstract: This paper introduces a multi-head spectral-attentive residual generative adversarial network for high-fidelity image haze removal with superior performance compared to existing methods.

title: Deep learning-assisted tactile sensing platform for efficient object classification and password recognition
journal: Journal of Materials Science and Technology
abstract: We develop a deep learning-assisted tactile sensing platform capable of efficient object classification and password recognition with high accuracy rates.

title: Examining the Sustainable Integration of Artificial Intelligence in Human Resource Digitalization in the Context of Industry 4.0
journal: European Public and Social Innovation Review
abstract: This study examines the sustainable integration of artificial intelligence in human resource digitalization within the context of Industry 4.0, identifying key challenges and opportunities.
